                                <layout><p>Text sits within carved and curved border, and is broken into three bands of letters at differing heights. The first two lines are large and monumental, the following nine are smaller, finished with a slightly larger two line-footer.</p>
                                    <rs ana="#execution.chiselled" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1">chiselled</rs>
