                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote><p>Letters are clear and neatly inscribed into the stone. Triangular interpuncts. Simple, neat, serifs. Tall "I" in lines 4, 7, 8, 10 in "IN", in line 9 in "REI", in line 10 in "EIUS", in line 11 in "ITEM", in line 12 in "COLLEGI".</p>
